config XIAOMI_HWID
	tristate "Xiaomi HWID driver"
	help
	  Reconstructed Xiaomi hardware ID module.

	  This driver exposes Xiaomi hardware/project identifiers through sysfs
	  and exported helper symbols used by vendor modules:

	    get_hw_build_adc
	    get_hw_country_version
	    get_hw_id_value
	    get_hw_project_adc
	    get_hw_version_build
	    get_hw_version_major
	    get_hw_version_minor
	    get_hw_version_platform
	    product_name_get

	  The original module depends on Qualcomm socinfo. If built on a kernel
	  where socinfo_get_id() is unavailable, provide an equivalent helper or
	  pass project=<id> as a module parameter and adapt hwid.c accordingly.
